  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Released 8/8/2018\u00a010:55 CT (15:55 UTC)</p><p><strong>Login &amp; Permissions Optimization</strong></p><p>We optimized the login screen and the permissions checking functions. There should be a noticeable load time improvement with the login, and\u00a0on most\u00a0list pages.</p><p><strong>Popover Updates</strong></p><p>Popovers\u00a0now auto-dismiss more effectively when you move your cursor away from the target.</p><p><strong>Dashboard Announcements</strong></p><p>We resolved an issue where Admins were unable to see announcements in some cases.</p><p><strong>Customer Add/Edit on Tickets</strong></p><p>We resolved an issue where the labels and values on the ticket screen would not always line up properly when adding/editing a customer from the ticket.</p><p>We also added the company name to\u00a0the customer view and the ticket view screens.</p><p><strong>Customer List Sorting</strong></p><p>We fixed an issue that would prevent sorting customers by columns while a name/phone number search was\u00a0applied.</p><p><strong>Pending Shipment Notifications</strong></p><p>We fixed an issue that prevented notifications for the &quot;Pending Shipment&quot;\u00a0shipment\u00a0status.</p><p><strong>Purchase Order Transfers with Markup</strong></p><p>We\u00a0fixed an issue where an unset cost markup percentage would result in a zero price.</p>",
      "representation": "export_view",
